learn what life is really about.

1122
01:10:07.374 --> 01:10:10.377
- Why? Why?

1123
01:10:10.511 --> 01:10:12.613
- You don't understand, Father.

1124
01:10:12.745 --> 01:10:16.283
Once they see what we've seen,
they'll be grateful.

1125
01:10:16.417 --> 01:10:19.053
They'll thank us.
You'll all thank us.

